1
00:00:00,630 --> 00:00:02,920
Sahaja Yoga is the synthesis of all the Yogas.

2
00:00:02,920 --> 00:00:10,950
Only thing [is] human beings have a wrong
notion that they can do something about it.

3
00:00:10,950 --> 00:00:12,540
It’s all built in them.

4
00:00:12,540 --> 00:00:18,480
Like any good instrument it’s all built
in and as soon as the Kundalini starts She

5
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:20,689
starts working it out.

6
00:00:20,689 --> 00:00:32,619
And all these gadgets within us go into motion
and they create that state within us by which

7
00:00:32,619 --> 00:00:37,400
the Kundalini rises within you.

8
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:48,510
Perhaps, we take it for granted, Kundalini
rising so much because we do not see all that’s

9
00:00:48,510 --> 00:00:49,660
happening within.

10
00:00:49,660 --> 00:00:56,580
(Talking to a mother with a child) Can you
take him out?

11
00:00:56,580 --> 00:01:02,150
He’s so happy that I don’t feel [he’s]
disturbing but everybody [else] is disturbed.

12
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:05,519
Rising of the Kundalini is the easiest for
Me.

13
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:07,170
No problem.

14
00:01:07,170 --> 00:01:16,810
Even working out those gadgets as I called
them – chakras and their different movements,

15
00:01:16,810 --> 00:01:22,740
constrictions and dilatation at a particular
point when Kundalini is coming up – is not

16
00:01:22,740 --> 00:01:24,140
difficult.

17
00:01:24,140 --> 00:01:32,840
But there are two other channels within us,
which you know very well, which act our sympathetic

18
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,249
nervous system.

19
00:01:34,249 --> 00:01:41,719
Which can be quite in trouble because of various
conditionings within us.

20
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:49,289
For example, some people have, say, a small
conditioning like going to a spiritualist.

21
00:01:49,289 --> 00:01:54,649
Take a position, a very simple thing like
going to a spiritualist.

22
00:01:54,649 --> 00:01:55,689
Now you ask the person, “Have you been to
a spiritualist?”

23
00:01:55,689 --> 00:02:02,319
Because if you find burning on the left Swadishthana
and the heart catching a little, it’s definitely

24
00:02:02,319 --> 00:02:05,789
he has been to somebody like that, which is
unauthorised.

25
00:02:05,789 --> 00:02:11,500
If you do something unauthorised you can feel
it on your Swadishthana, that the person has

26
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:12,500
been there.

27
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:20,740
Now see, just say that he has been there,
to a spiritualist, you can work it out by

28
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:23,340
giving the bandhan to the spiritualist whose
name he might tell.

29
00:02:23,340 --> 00:02:25,430
Even if he doesn’t tell it can work out.

30
00:02:25,430 --> 00:02:28,980
It is that subtle and it works that subtle.

31
00:02:28,980 --> 00:02:30,490
But that much one has to say.

32
00:02:30,490 --> 00:02:36,780
Now, the reason for all this is this: that
at this stage when you are getting Realisation,

33
00:02:36,780 --> 00:02:43,720
you are human beings, the highest that the
Creation has created, highest.

34
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:48,900
And that you have the freedom to choose the
Good or the Bad.

35
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:52,810
This choice must be made by you.

36
00:02:52,810 --> 00:02:58,260
If you make that willing choice, then Kundalini
is the easiest thing for Me or for anyone

37
00:02:58,260 --> 00:02:59,880
of you.

38
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:04,320
But if there is hesitation about it, for example,
a person may say, “Oh, so what’s wrong?

39
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:07,540
I went only for one day."

40
00:03:07,540 --> 00:03:10,250
Anything like that, Kundalini goes back.

41
00:03:10,250 --> 00:03:18,010
She is a sensitive thing, extremely sensitive:
any kind of refusal to Her or denial to Her

42
00:03:18,010 --> 00:03:20,990
She goes down.

43
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:29,370
And this is something if you understand that
we are human beings and we are the highest,

44
00:03:29,370 --> 00:03:32,210
highest in the Creation.

45
00:03:32,210 --> 00:03:35,560
We have no self-esteem, I tell you.

46
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,900
Human beings have no self-esteem.

47
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:40,750
If they had, they would not have behaved like
this.

48
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:48,030
The way we are torturing ourselves, torturing
others, I mean doing all kinds of nonsense.

49
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:52,390
If they had that understanding of themselves
there would have been no problem, but they

50
00:03:52,390 --> 00:03:53,390
do not have.

51
00:03:53,390 --> 00:03:58,160
Only when it comes to Kundalini, then they
have all their esteem.

52
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,360
Most surprising!

53
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:02,950
Then they will say, “Why not?

54
00:04:02,950 --> 00:04:04,150
What’s wrong?”

55
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:06,910
Anything you say that time, that’s the time
they should be most surrendering, that’s

56
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:07,910
the time they’ll argue!

57
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:08,910
It’s human nature!

58
00:04:08,910 --> 00:04:16,519
Otherwise they will not argue, if you ask
them, “Will you come to the pub?”

59
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,980
“Yes, why not?”

60
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,440
They’ll never argue.

61
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:21,690
Have you heard anybody saying that?

62
00:04:21,690 --> 00:04:26,170
Me even, I mean I tell you, I dare not.

63
00:04:26,170 --> 00:04:30,610
Say, people come to My house for a party and
thing, My husband has to offer them drinks

64
00:04:30,610 --> 00:04:35,040
because they won’t talk to us if you do
not offer them drinks.

65
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,040
That’s the thing in England.

66
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:41,020
In India I never would allow anybody to even
bring any bottles in the house.

67
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:43,930
But here they said, “English won’t talk
to you if you don’t have bottles in the

68
00:04:43,930 --> 00:04:44,930
house!

69
00:04:44,930 --> 00:04:47,510
How can you do it, it’s not a house if there
is no bottle!”

70
00:04:47,510 --> 00:04:51,650
That’s the part of the culture, the base
of it.

71
00:04:51,650 --> 00:04:53,170
But I dare not say even once.

72
00:04:53,170 --> 00:04:55,230
They will say “Why don’t you drink?

73
00:04:55,230 --> 00:04:57,410
Is it not allowed in your religion?

74
00:04:57,410 --> 00:04:59,670
Why don’t you drink?”

75
00:04:59,670 --> 00:05:04,750
But if I say, “Why do you drink?”, finished!

76
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:05,750
I have no manners.

77
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:06,750
(Laughter) I am most unmannerly person going
round!

78
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:07,750
You see My point?

79
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:13,370
You are not supposed to say these things,
you are not supposed to discuss these things.

80
00:05:13,370 --> 00:05:19,150
But if you say some sort of a dirty joke,
really everybody will be very happy.

81
00:05:19,150 --> 00:05:23,360
There is nothing like indecency indecorum
in those things.

82
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:27,320
But it is indecent to say something decent!

83
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:33,770
In the same way in Kundalini it happens that
when it comes to actual Kundalini rising,

84
00:05:33,770 --> 00:05:36,910
one should be in the most humble manner, “Oh,
God!”

85
00:05:36,910 --> 00:05:40,870
Just see the time, the moment has come for
you to get what it is.

86
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:44,541
That time they’ll be arrogantly like this,
you see, sitting, “No, it doesn’t happen

87
00:05:44,541 --> 00:05:45,541
to me!”

88
00:05:45,541 --> 00:05:48,740
As if it’s a very great thing it’s not
happening to you!

89
00:05:48,740 --> 00:05:49,740
Just imagine!

90
00:05:49,740 --> 00:05:56,220
It would be like a king sitting on a throne
and somebody is trying to put the crown on

91
00:05:56,220 --> 00:06:01,480
the head and the person says, “Oh, it doesn’t
fit me at all!”

92
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,460
It’s that silly, you know.

93
00:06:03,460 --> 00:06:05,490
But it is so.

94
00:06:05,490 --> 00:06:13,000
And this is why the Kundalini, the Kundalini
doesn’t rise and She stops.

95
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:24,790
And once She is that way, little bit insulted
She feels hesitant.

96
00:06:24,790 --> 00:06:30,390
You see, like a guest who has come into your
house, if you put a punch on the nose, it

97
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:36,820
will take time for you to patch up the whole
thing, isn’t it?

98
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:42,890
And that patching up is just so slow, I mean
people just don’t believe in patching up

99
00:06:42,890 --> 00:06:43,890
anything.

100
00:06:43,890 --> 00:06:47,430
And that’s why the Kundalini is so disturbing.

101
00:06:47,430 --> 00:06:50,280
It is so disturbing.

102
00:06:50,280 --> 00:07:01,699
One should understand that She is extremely
sensitive, She is your self-respect.

103
00:07:01,699 --> 00:07:09,550
Any fun you make out of Her is a waste: you
are wasting yourself, you are wasting the

104
00:07:09,550 --> 00:07:18,040
energy of the Kundalini, you are stopping
your Realisation.

105
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:22,350
It is very important to understand that She
is Knowledge.

106
00:07:22,350 --> 00:07:26,419
Whatever you have read so far is not knowledge,
is Avidya.

107
00:07:26,419 --> 00:07:29,210
Humility must come to you for that, very important.

108
00:07:29,210 --> 00:07:33,090
You might have read thousands of books, makes
no difference to the Kundalini.

109
00:07:33,090 --> 00:07:38,729
She is Knowledge.

110
00:07:38,729 --> 00:07:41,900
That time all your knowledge will come, “Mother,
I’ve read in this book this is written,

111
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:43,020
that is written,” Finished!

112
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:45,770
[Then] your Realisation is a very difficult
thing.

113
00:07:45,770 --> 00:07:52,310
I’m here sitting down, “Oh please, have
your Realisation, don’t disturb Her”.

114
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:57,070
I’m sitting in between like a mediator,
you see, between Her and you, “Now, don’t

115
00:07:57,070 --> 00:07:58,070
disturb Her”.

116
00:07:58,070 --> 00:08:02,240
Here you are, suddenly you come out with a
special announcement that, “I’ve read

117
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:06,370
such and such book” and that book must be
from some bhoot or somebody horrible, has

118
00:08:06,370 --> 00:08:07,380
to be.

119
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:13,870
And then you come out, “I’ve read that
book and such and such, it says so…”,

120
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:14,979
finished.

121
00:08:14,979 --> 00:08:23,840
Here we are talking of actualisation, of getting
Realisation, not of books.

122
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:26,380
You have to forget what you have been going
through.

123
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:31,009
You have to forget what you have been doing
so far for Kundalini.

124
00:08:31,009 --> 00:08:36,890
You have to forget all those things you have
had so far through your gurus and this and

125
00:08:36,890 --> 00:08:38,310
that, and all other sorts of nonsense.

126
00:08:38,310 --> 00:08:44,630
You have to forget all that and you have to
think it’s a very simple abode of your Mother

127
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:49,110
where you have come just to have your food.

128
00:08:49,110 --> 00:08:53,160
Please come and be seated and have your food.

129
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:57,670
With that simplicity of heart only, the Kundalini
will react.

130
00:08:57,670 --> 00:09:02,540
If you are a lord of some place, Kundalini
will say “Alright, go and be a lord."

131
00:09:02,540 --> 00:09:04,360
Kundalini is not bothered about you.

132
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:10,510
She knows who is arrogant, She knows who is
humble, She knows who wants Realisation.

133
00:09:10,510 --> 00:09:15,170
She has been recording everything what you
have been doing since long, since ages, since

134
00:09:15,170 --> 00:09:16,540
many lives.

135
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:17,540
So She knows everything.

136
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:23,890
And if She even now finds the same thing,
She just refuses to rise.

137
00:09:23,890 --> 00:09:29,890
I’ve seen it’s a common experience: if
somebody doesn’t get Realisation, he feels

138
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:31,230
very proud, “Oh, I’m not mesmerised!”

139
00:09:31,230 --> 00:09:37,290
I said, “Is it mesmerism, is it?”

140
00:09:37,290 --> 00:09:48,839
If through mesmerism you could cure cancer,
then I think mesmerism is a good idea, if

141
00:09:48,839 --> 00:09:52,279
it is mesmerism! (laughing)

142
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:58,779
So first of all, before getting Realisation,
one has to know that this is what you are

143
00:09:58,779 --> 00:10:05,450
seeking, this is what you have to have and
the Kundalini is the only thing that is going

144
00:10:05,450 --> 00:10:06,480
to transform you.

145
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,820
There’s no doubt about it.

146
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:15,150
But even when you come to that point of Kundalini,
people have read books on Kundalini also.

147
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:19,740
And everything they’ve read, already, they
have sorted out everything already!

148
00:10:19,740 --> 00:10:26,660
So, then they ask, “Then what about that
book?

149
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:27,660
It says so…”

150
00:10:27,660 --> 00:10:31,110
Now you see for yourself, why don’t you
see what it is like!

151
00:10:31,110 --> 00:10:33,050
But in seeing also you have to be humble.

152
00:10:33,050 --> 00:10:38,220
Those people who have come to us with humility,
with innocence, have got Realisation very

153
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:39,820
well, and they’ve established it.

154
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:48,730
They have got it at a time, some of them,
who were just dying, just dying, they came

155
00:10:48,730 --> 00:10:53,850
to Me at the time they were in coma.

156
00:10:53,850 --> 00:10:58,140
But they have established themselves because
they were true seekers.

157
00:10:58,140 --> 00:11:01,320
If you have to seek the Truth, you have to
be truthful also.

158
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:05,050
And if you are truthful you will see that
this is truthful.

159
00:11:05,050 --> 00:11:09,850
There is no hanky-panky in Sahaja Yoga, you
cannot have.

160
00:11:09,850 --> 00:11:13,250
There is no befooling or anything.

161
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:15,259
That’s not possible.

162
00:11:15,259 --> 00:11:21,980
The Kundalini has to rise, She has to give
you Realisation, She has to get you alright.

163
00:11:21,980 --> 00:11:24,000
No other certificate is needed.

164
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:30,770
This is the main certificate you have to have
– that you get your Realisation, you feel

165
00:11:30,770 --> 00:11:32,290
your vibrations, not others.

166
00:11:32,290 --> 00:11:34,290
Some other people can feel it.

167
00:11:34,290 --> 00:11:39,400
The other day we had a very unique experience
and there was a gentleman and the Kundalini

168
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:45,830
was trying to push the Sahasrara and the whole
Grace was flowing on him as if like a fountain

169
00:11:45,830 --> 00:11:49,530
coming out of here, and nothing was going
into his being.

170
00:11:49,530 --> 00:11:51,110
Can you imagine!

171
00:11:51,110 --> 00:11:54,860
The Grace, just pouring onto that dumb fellow.

172
00:11:54,860 --> 00:11:57,600
It was all falling on all the sides but nothing
going into him!

173
00:11:57,600 --> 00:12:00,750
And the fellow was very proud, “Oh, nothing
is happening to me!”you see.

174
00:12:00,750 --> 00:12:02,269
I said, “Look at this man!”

175
00:12:02,269 --> 00:12:04,240
The Grace has to be accepted.

176
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:09,880
With folded hands one has to get it.

177
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:11,410
With humility.

178
00:12:11,410 --> 00:12:23,190
How can we be arrogant when the Grace is coming
on you?

179
00:12:23,190 --> 00:12:29,970
Is it sensible, is that good manners, by any
chance?

180
00:12:29,970 --> 00:12:35,000
One has to be extremely humble.

181
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:40,100
That will show to the Kundalini that you want
it, that you want to have it.

182
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:50,050
At the smallest of points it has been stopped.

183
00:12:50,050 --> 00:12:56,899
Like I would say, if a little thing goes into
the eyes, you cannot see the whole sky.

184
00:12:56,899 --> 00:13:03,310
In the same way, a very small thing, a very,
very small thing can stop the movement of

185
00:13:03,310 --> 00:13:06,190
the Kundalini.

186
00:13:06,190 --> 00:13:10,089
And that small thing, if somebody says, “Ask
this question.

187
00:13:10,089 --> 00:13:13,300
Please ask and get it.

188
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:21,880
This is your due,” you have to just, to
be humble.

189
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,410
If you cannot be humble it is not going to
work out.

190
00:13:23,410 --> 00:13:36,750
That’s something so simple but it’s difficult
for people to be simple.

191
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:45,340
Seeker: The word ‘humble’ is misunderstood
in England, I think, a lot.

192
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:47,161
Does humble mean “no intellectual arrogance”?

193
00:13:47,161 --> 00:13:48,161
Shri Mataji: No intellectual arrogance?

194
00:13:48,161 --> 00:13:49,161
Is a good idea, I tell you!

195
00:13:49,161 --> 00:13:50,161
Intellectual arrogance now…

196
00:13:50,161 --> 00:13:51,161
Can you open the windows, please?

197
00:13:51,161 --> 00:13:52,161
Windows a little bit more.

198
00:13:52,161 --> 00:13:53,240
That you can open.

199
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:55,390
There are so many people are here.

200
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:57,120
…that’s a good idea!

201
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,850
Now, let’s see intellectuals.

202
00:13:58,850 --> 00:13:59,850
Oh, God!

203
00:13:59,850 --> 00:14:01,270
I’ve had enough of them!

204
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:07,800
(laughing) Even the name gives you heat, I
tell you.

205
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:12,370
Now, let’s see the intellectuals, the rationality.

206
00:14:12,370 --> 00:14:15,630
Rationality has lead us where?

207
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:18,240
Just think over it.

208
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:22,670
Rationality is nothing but your brain’s
own imagination.

209
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:25,640
You can rationalise everything.

210
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,120
“What’s wrong?”

211
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:30,089
What’s wrong in anything?

212
00:14:30,089 --> 00:14:33,149
People are killing their own children, “What’s
wrong?

213
00:14:33,149 --> 00:14:34,829
What’s wrong, tell Me?

214
00:14:34,829 --> 00:14:36,089
Basically, what’s wrong?”

215
00:14:36,089 --> 00:14:40,040
I mean, they are their own children, they
have produced it, they are killing it, they

216
00:14:40,040 --> 00:14:41,560
can produce more, what’s wrong?

217
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:46,740
Tomorrow, you will be amazed, there will be
people coming out to say that, “If we kill

218
00:14:46,740 --> 00:14:49,860
our children you have no business to say anything!”

219
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:57,630
People will come and fight the law that, “If
they are our children we can kill them.

220
00:14:57,630 --> 00:14:58,850
We have produced them.

221
00:14:58,850 --> 00:15:00,850
We can produce more children.

222
00:15:00,850 --> 00:15:01,959
What’s wrong?”

223
00:15:01,959 --> 00:15:08,570
You see, rationality can give all kinds of
absurd ideas.

224
00:15:08,570 --> 00:15:12,870
But it is not wisdom.

225
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:18,610
It is not wisdom, it’s not logical.

226
00:15:18,610 --> 00:15:22,370
Everything has to be logical.

227
00:15:22,370 --> 00:15:28,420
Sahaja Yoga is Absolute logic.

228
00:15:28,420 --> 00:15:34,149
Rationality is limited, but logic is not.

