00:36:44,029 --> 00:36:50,540
Humble because so far you have not known what
is the Truth or the Reality is.

457
00:36:50,540 --> 00:36:58,490
To know it you have to be humble, because
it doesn’t come to you out of arrogance.

458
00:36:58,490 --> 00:37:04,979
It comes through, it penetrates in you, it
sieves through you if you are humble, otherwise

459
00:37:04,979 --> 00:37:05,979
it does not.

460
00:37:05,979 --> 00:37:06,979
I am warning you!

461
00:37:06,979 --> 00:37:08,349
It does not.

462
00:37:08,349 --> 00:37:13,670
It doesn’t go to arrogant people and to
aggressive people, it doesn’t work out in

463
00:37:13,670 --> 00:37:21,769
them, it only works out among humble people.

464
00:37:21,769 --> 00:37:25,309
Try to be humble in your heart.

465
00:37:25,309 --> 00:37:28,809
We enjoy your humility.

466
00:37:28,809 --> 00:37:30,359
You really enjoy your humility.

467
00:37:30,359 --> 00:37:34,049
Actually humility gives you innocence.

468
00:37:34,049 --> 00:37:38,729
Humility is the only way to achieve our lost
innocence.

469
00:37:38,729 --> 00:37:47,559
Even if you have all the powers of the world
and you are humble, how beautiful you look!

470
00:37:47,559 --> 00:37:56,380
Any person who is in a big position and if
he is humble, people write legends after such

471
00:37:56,380 --> 00:37:58,660
a personality.

472
00:37:58,660 --> 00:38:07,019
Try to develop a humble attitude towards life,
extremely humble.

473
00:38:07,019 --> 00:38:13,219
But with humility we confuse inertia, that’s
a wrong thing.

474
00:38:13,219 --> 00:38:22,599
Humility never means inertia, humility means
dynamism.

475
00:38:22,599 --> 00:38:27,650
And that dynamism is extremely quiet, silent
and beautiful.

476
00:38:27,650 --> 00:38:33,710
Sahaja Yoga is a tremendous thing, it’s
Mahayoga.

477
00:38:33,710 --> 00:38:44,299
At this stage it is Mahayoga, because it has
reached it’s highest peak now.

478
00:38:44,299 --> 00:38:48,599
Never in any incarnation so many realisations
were given.

479
00:38:48,599 --> 00:38:56,859
Krishna used to do Sahaja Yog, He used to
raise Kundalini, Rama did that, Christ did

480
00:38:56,859 --> 00:39:00,799
it, Buddha did it, Mahavira did it.

481
00:39:00,799 --> 00:39:04,069
Nobody could achieve mass realisation.

482
00:39:04,069 --> 00:39:11,579
Today it’s so fortunate that I am facing
so many saints.

483
00:39:11,579 --> 00:39:18,930
It’s My great faith and great fortune that
you all have got Realisation.

484
00:39:18,930 --> 00:39:25,700
You don’t know, My joy has no words to express
itself.

485
00:39:25,700 --> 00:39:36,479
But let not this garden be ruined by abandonment
and by foolishness.

486
00:39:36,479 --> 00:39:39,469
It is tender, newly blossoming, beautiful
garden.

487
00:39:39,469 --> 00:39:45,650
Look after it with that care and gentleness.

488
00:39:45,650 --> 00:39:55,650
Otherwise it can all fritter away.

489
00:39:55,650 --> 00:39:58,869
Most of the fake gurus are being exposed now.

490
00:39:58,869 --> 00:40:00,470
They are all going to be exposed.

491
00:40:00,470 --> 00:40:04,609
They’ll fritter away because they are false.

492
00:40:04,609 --> 00:40:10,170
But if Sahaja Yoga fritters away, you English
Sahaja Yogis will be held responsible because

493
00:40:10,170 --> 00:40:12,569
of your inertia or your arrogance.

494
00:40:12,569 --> 00:40:18,729
When you are active you are arrogant, when
you are not you are lethargic.

495
00:40:18,729 --> 00:40:24,170
Please, come out of these two extremes.

496
00:40:24,170 --> 00:40:35,299
I request you to meditate on this about yourself
and I’m sure we are going to achieve wonders,

497
00:40:35,299 --> 00:40:36,670
definitely, no doubt about it.

498
00:40:36,670 --> 00:40:40,279
May God bless you all

499
00:40:40,279 --> 00:40:51,289
Those who have come for the first time, I
would request them to come in front so that

500
00:40:51,289 --> 00:40:52,960
we can see them, all of them.

